column5: still looking for a tiller fishing boat. Somebody out there must need to sell me one.Motor or not,drop me a line.
What type of boat do you want? A plain bench seat boat or one with carpeted floors and pedestal seats.
A regular fishing boat with a open floor plan. Example: lund pro guide,alaskan. crestliner etc. Newer or older, a decent all around fishing boat.
